title: Voxit SpeakApp 2.6.0.1030 incl. keygen
description:
Voxit SpeakApp is a program developed in Sweden which will convert text to speech. Apart from all the Nordic languages, many other languages are supported such as British English, American English, German, French and Spanish.

The program has a Swedish, Norwegian and English UI.
Supported operative systems are Windows XP, Vista, 7 and 8 / 8.1, both 32 and 64 bits.

More information here (in Swedish):
www.voxit.se/budgiepro/default.asp?s=voicex


(P.S. The keygen might give your AV software a false positive.)
